Construction engineering quality inspectors conduct a safety inspection of a tower crane at a construction site in Changxing County, East China's Zhejiang Province on Wednesday. The county has launched a campaign to entrust industry professionals with special checks of heavy-lifting machines, especially heavily used tower cranes and building hoists that have been in service for a long time, in an effort to ensure construction site safety. Photo: VCGÂ  
